{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "8.120", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Frau Pr\u00e4sidentin! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "8.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.800", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.840", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Situation in Afghanistan sieht schlimmer aus, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.840", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "als das hier bisher beschrieben wurde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "21.280", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Laut den Vereinten Nationen sind 360\u00a0000\u00a0Menschen innerhalb von Afghanistan auf der Flucht\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "21.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.480", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und in den Nachbarl\u00e4ndern Iran und Pakistan weitere Millionen Fl\u00fcchtlinge. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.640", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "3,3\u00a0Millionen Menschen sind in Afghanistan auf humanit\u00e4re Hilfe angewiesen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.880", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "2017 kamen 3\u00a0500\u00a0Zivilisten ums Leben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.680", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bisher hat dieser Krieg dort 150\u00a0000\u00a0Tote gefordert."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.200", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben von der Bundesregierung einen \u201ePerspektivbericht Afghanistan\u201c vorgelegt bekommen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "50.800", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist interessant. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "50.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.760", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Fr\u00fcher hie\u00df dieser Bericht \u201eFortschrittsbericht Afghanistan\u201c. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.080", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ein kleiner realistischer Schritt hin zu der Erkenntnis, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "61.080", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass es offensichtlich keinen Fortschritt gibt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "61.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.680", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser Perspektivbericht enth\u00e4lt eine ganze Reihe von sehr bemerkenswerten Informationen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.800", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist dort zum Beispiel zu lesen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "70.480", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Lage in Afghanistan gepr\u00e4gt sei durch:"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "70.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.760", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unzureichende Effektivit\u00e4t der staatlichen Verwaltung und Sicherheitskr\u00e4fte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "78.880", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "verst\u00e4rkte Angriffe der Taliban sowie von IS-Gruppen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "78.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.600", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Korruption, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.160", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Armut und Arbeitslosigkeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.720", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Flucht und Migration\u00a0\u2026"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "83.520", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kampfhandlungen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "83.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "90.440", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Anschl\u00e4ge und Entf\u00fchrungsgefahr erlauben Investitionen und Beratungsleistungen nur noch unter strengen Sicherheitsvorkehrungen\u00a0..."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "90.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "94.520", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das waren beides Zitate aus dem Perspektivbericht der Bundesregierung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "94.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "96.520", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Um es klar zu \u00fcbersetzen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "96.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.200", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Entwicklungshilfe in Afghanistan ist nahezu unm\u00f6glich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.000", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "112.640", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in diese Situation hinein will die Bundesregierung mehr Soldaten nach Afghanistan schicken als bisher. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "112.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.800", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch da ist interessant, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.120", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was dazu im Perspektivbericht steht: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.880", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundeswehr k\u00f6nne nur die H\u00e4lfte der vereinbarten Ausbildungsverpflichtungen durchf\u00fchren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.120", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und der Schutz der Ausbilder sei nicht gew\u00e4hrleistet.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "126.960", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "126.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.280", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn ich feststelle, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "131.160", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass ein Einsatz nicht funktioniert, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "131.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.800", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann verst\u00e4rke ich ihn doch nicht dadurch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "134.480", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "indem ich noch mehr Soldatinnen und Soldaten hinschicke, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "134.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.840", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern ziehe daraus die Konsequenzen und sage: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "144.760", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Bundeswehr muss aus Afghanistan abzogen werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "144.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.600", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Offensichtlich ist es so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.880", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die Bundeswehrsoldaten hier nicht hilfreich sind."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "155.760", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Sicherheitslage in Kabul ist so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "155.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.320", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die deutsche Botschaft nicht arbeitsf\u00e4hig ist. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "161.760", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die GIZ hat ihre B\u00fcros geschlossen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "161.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.080", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist insgesamt so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.880", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Afghaninnen und Afghanen die Situation vor Ort sehr deutlich beschreiben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "171.880", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich will ganz kurz Malalai Joya zitieren: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "171.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.440", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Afghanistan ist durch und durch korrupt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.440", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Milliarden US-Dollar kamen von der sogenannten internationalen Gemeinschaft\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.000", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "f\u00fcr Bildung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.920", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den Wiederaufbau, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.440", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Waisenbetreuung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "185.480", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das meiste Geld ist aber in die Taschen von Warlords geflossen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "185.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.880", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Und Afghanistan ist heute der schlimmste Ort auf Erden f\u00fcr Frauen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.800", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich finde das alles schon sehr heftig. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.160", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Angesichts dieser Situationsbeschreibung kann ich nur sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.040", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es ist und bleibt falsch, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.720", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Bundeswehrsoldaten wegen der sogenannten Sicherheitslage nach Afghanistan geschickt werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.800", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber zugleich Menschen von hier aus nach Afghanistan abgeschoben werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "222.760", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir als Linke sagen sowohl Nein zu der Stationierung von Bundeswehrsoldaten in Afghanistan als auch Nein zur Abschiebung von Menschen von hier aus nach Afghanistan."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "222.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.840", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "226.200", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "226.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "227.680", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Tobias Pfl\u00fcger.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "227.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.920", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der n\u00e4chste Redner: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.960", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Omid Nouripour f\u00fcr B\u00fcndnis\u00a090/Die Gr\u00fcnen."
   ]
  }
 ]
